==English==

===Noun===
'''hypallage'''
# A [[literary]] [[device]] that is the [[reversal]] of the [[syntactic]] [[relation]] of two words, e.g. "her beauty's face" or ''I can't knock the smirk of his stupid face'' (because the thing that is referred to being stupid is "him", and not "his face"). 

